title: UFYB Bonus: My Story
itunes:title: UFYB Bonus: My Story
description:
Today, I'm going doing something a little bit different. As our flock grows, I know that some of you may not know much about me or my story - where I came from. So today I'm going to share with you a little bit about me. I'm sharing this with you so that you can see that where you are now, the heaviness you feel, the pressure, does not have to be your future reality.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/my-story-2
